# What is firebase, 

--->  so firebase is a platform developed by google that provides a suite of tools that helps programmers to develop and build web and mobile applications 
      without working on backend. 
      it provides fetures that help in building web and mobile application...
      
      features:
        # authentication,
        # firebase store,
        # real-time database,

##1) Implementaion of fire base Authentication.

      import {GoogleAuthProvider,getAuth} from "firebase/auth"
      
      // initialise getAuth() by providing app in it 
      const auth = getAuth(app)
      
      // create the instance of GoogleAuthProvider
      const provider = new GoogleAuthProvider

      // export both auth and provider

